        "TileImage": "$($repository d2e845c3-6817-485d-801b-449a0eb3d8c9).Image",
        "Description": "Good Afternoon, \r\rA bit of field testing today, 47. R&amp;D needs you to test some explosive devices to assess effectiveness and deployment ease. Based on your  feedback, R&amp;D will do some spring cleaning on our inventory, retiring the least efficient tools.\r\rGood luck as always.\r\n\r\n<HCCE>",
